1
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:55,000
"Lost To You"

2
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:57,700
(Episode 11)

3
00:00:58,800 --> 00:01:01,299
When the world is on
the brink of destruction,

4
00:01:01,300 --> 00:01:03,799
I finally realize

5
00:01:03,800 --> 00:01:05,999
I only want to save

6
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:08,200
the corner where you are.

7
00:01:14,916 --> 00:01:15,916
Leave Zhan Wang.

8
00:01:16,750 --> 00:01:17,750
Never contact him again.

9
00:01:18,666 --> 00:01:19,666
Uncle,

10
00:01:20,125 --> 00:01:21,125
My meeting with you today

11
00:01:21,375 --> 00:01:22,415
wasn't to negotiate terms.

12
00:01:24,583 --> 00:01:25,583
This isn't a discussion.

13
00:01:26,333 --> 00:01:27,333
It's a notification.

14
00:01:27,625 --> 00:01:28,625
And a deal.

15
00:01:29,125 --> 00:01:30,125
I've looked into it.

16
00:01:30,500 --> 00:01:31,750
Your mother's shop

17
00:01:32,375 --> 00:01:33,375
is struggling,

18
00:01:33,625 --> 00:01:34,625
and barely getting by.

19
00:01:35,041 --> 00:01:36,041
Furthermore,

20
00:01:36,333 --> 00:01:37,333
the apartment you live in

21
00:01:37,791 --> 00:01:38,791
belongs to my mother.

22
00:01:38,958 --> 00:01:40,758
Even though the title
was transferred to you,

23
00:01:41,375 --> 00:01:42,375
I believe

24
00:01:42,875 --> 00:01:43,875
I have the power

25
00:01:44,291 --> 00:01:45,625
to take it back.

26
00:01:46,291 --> 00:01:47,083
I can set your mother up

27
00:01:47,208 --> 00:01:48,791
with a shop in a better location,

28
00:01:49,583 --> 00:01:50,767
guaranteeing a steady stream of customers.

29
00:01:50,791 --> 00:01:52,517
I can also help your
sister, who loves acting,

30
00:01:52,541 --> 00:01:53,125
go to Jingzhou

31
00:01:53,250 --> 00:01:54,809
to pursue her dream of becoming an actress.

32
00:01:54,833 --> 00:01:55,833
Or,

33
00:01:56,250 --> 00:01:58,208
I can make things much harder for you.

34
00:01:59,250 --> 00:02:01,500
Hard enough to run your
mother out of business,

35
00:02:02,250 --> 00:02:04,041
and ensure that apartment

36
00:02:04,166 --> 00:02:05,791
never truly becomes yours.

37
00:02:06,333 --> 00:02:07,333
Uncle,

38
00:02:08,250 --> 00:02:09,458
are you threatening me?

39
00:02:10,958 --> 00:02:12,666
I'm just showing you reality.

40
00:02:13,916 --> 00:02:16,583
Love is not a luxury

41
00:02:17,250 --> 00:02:18,666
that people your age can afford.

42
00:02:19,666 --> 00:02:20,708
Zhan Wang's life

43
00:02:21,083 --> 00:02:23,613
shouldn't be dragged down
by such an unstable relationship.

44
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:26,000
Especially now,

45
00:02:26,208 --> 00:02:27,958
his condition requires better medical care

46
00:02:28,458 --> 00:02:29,083
and absolute focus,

47
00:02:29,458 --> 00:02:31,041
without any distractions.

48
00:02:31,291 --> 00:02:31,916
And you

49
00:02:32,083 --> 00:02:34,083
are clearly the biggest distraction.

50
00:02:36,833 --> 00:02:37,833
Take this money,

51
00:02:38,208 --> 00:02:39,958
solve your family's immediate problems,

52
00:02:41,125 --> 00:02:42,125
and leave Zhan Wang.

53
00:02:42,333 --> 00:02:44,041
For you and your mother,

54
00:02:44,750 --> 00:02:47,208
this is the wisest choice right now.

55
00:02:47,750 --> 00:02:48,750
And for him,

56
00:02:50,416 --> 00:02:52,166
it lifts an unnecessary burden.

57
00:02:52,875 --> 00:02:53,875
It's a win-win.

58
00:02:57,291 --> 00:02:57,833
Uncle,

59
00:02:58,208 --> 00:03:00,048
you have the power to
take everything from me??

60
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:02,583
my shop, my home.

61
00:03:05,291 --> 00:03:07,731
But you can't take away my
determination to stay by his side.

62
00:03:08,291 --> 00:03:09,651
You can solve anything with money.

63
00:03:10,041 --> 00:03:11,041
Perhaps

64
00:03:11,250 --> 00:03:12,690
you can buy him better medical care,

65
00:03:13,875 --> 00:03:15,475
but you can't give him a reason to live.

66
00:03:15,958 --> 00:03:16,958
But I can.

67
00:03:17,333 --> 00:03:18,333
So, I won't leave.

68
00:03:19,458 --> 00:03:20,458
The money,

69
00:03:20,625 --> 00:03:21,250
please take it back.

70
00:03:21,583 --> 00:03:23,263
I will be there when he goes into surgery,

71
00:03:23,458 --> 00:03:24,978
and I'll be waiting when he comes out.

72
00:03:25,875 --> 00:03:26,875
As for everything else,

73
00:03:29,083 --> 00:03:30,166
as his father,

74
00:03:31,409 --> 00:03:32,969
you can do whatever you think is right.

75
00:03:33,687 --> 00:03:35,007
But I won't be the one to let go.

76
00:03:35,541 --> 00:03:36,541
This is my decision,

77
00:03:37,375 --> 00:03:38,615
and I don't need your approval.

78
00:03:58,250 --> 00:03:59,250
I knew

79
00:03:59,666 --> 00:04:00,666
you'd find me.

80
00:04:01,416 --> 00:04:02,856
Why did you run out of the hospital?

81
00:04:03,083 --> 00:04:04,123
I've been in bed for days.

82
00:04:04,291 --> 00:04:05,371
My bones were getting rusty.

83
00:04:08,875 --> 00:04:09,875
Come on.

84
00:04:10,750 --> 00:04:11,750
Spar with me.

85
00:04:15,750 --> 00:04:16,750
But in your condition,

86
00:04:17,250 --> 00:04:18,930
you shouldn't be doing strenuous exercise.

87
00:04:26,500 --> 00:04:27,860
My dad came to see you, didn't he?

88
00:04:30,583 --> 00:04:31,583
Let me hear it.

89
00:04:32,291 --> 00:04:33,291
How much am I worth?

90
00:04:34,583 --> 00:04:35,583
A lot.

91
00:04:36,583 --> 00:04:38,183
Enough for my family to buy a new house,

92
00:04:38,875 --> 00:04:39,875
open a new shop,

93
00:04:40,791 --> 00:04:42,151
and fund my sister's acting dream.

94
00:04:44,833 --> 00:04:45,833
I didn't realize

95
00:04:46,333 --> 00:04:47,375
I was worth that much.

96
00:04:48,791 --> 00:04:49,791
That's good.

97
00:04:50,541 --> 00:04:52,221
At least I could leave you with something.

98
00:04:54,166 --> 00:04:55,166
I didn't take it.

99
00:05:02,875 --> 00:05:03,875
I don't want money.

100
00:05:05,708 --> 00:05:07,583
I want to stay with a big
jerk named Zhan Wang

101
00:05:09,208 --> 00:05:10,208
until he gets better.

102
00:05:12,958 --> 00:05:13,958
Do you know

103
00:05:14,833 --> 00:05:16,333
how risky this surgery is?

104
00:05:16,416 --> 00:05:17,416
So what?

105
00:05:22,875 --> 00:05:23,875
Zhan Wang,

106
00:05:24,833 --> 00:05:25,833
listen to me.

107
00:05:26,750 --> 00:05:27,950
I don't need you to be a hero,

108
00:05:29,201 --> 00:05:30,921
nor do I want you to
give up so tragically.

109
00:05:32,500 --> 00:05:33,500
I want you to try again

110
00:05:35,125 --> 00:05:36,125
for my sake.

111
00:05:42,708 --> 00:05:43,916
I really can't say no to you.

112
00:05:45,208 --> 00:05:46,208
Okay.

113
00:05:46,583 --> 00:05:47,583
For you,

114
00:05:47,791 --> 00:05:48,791
I'll try again.

115
00:05:50,125 --> 00:05:51,125
Then,

116
00:05:51,166 --> 00:05:52,226
let's go back to the hospital.

117
00:05:52,250 --> 00:05:53,250
What's the rush?

118
00:05:53,583 --> 00:05:54,863
One day won't make a difference.

119
00:05:55,291 --> 00:05:56,291
I want to make

120
00:05:56,750 --> 00:05:58,070
some beautiful memories with you.

121
00:05:58,375 --> 00:05:59,375
What?

122
00:06:01,125 --> 00:06:01,541
Let's go.

123
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,000
I'll take you somewhere.

124
00:06:11,875 --> 00:06:12,875
Why are we here?

125
00:06:13,625 --> 00:06:15,708
I just wanted to take a photo.

126
00:06:17,083 --> 00:06:18,208
Surprise, Bro!

127
00:06:20,208 --> 00:06:21,500
After Brother Zhan Wang told me,

128
00:06:21,583 --> 00:06:23,183
I've been planning this for a long time.

129
00:06:23,458 --> 00:06:25,018
Lin Xia helped me pick out the clothes.

130
00:06:25,375 --> 00:06:26,750
Today, we'll definitely

131
00:06:26,833 --> 00:06:29,041
get the best couple's photoshoot.

132
00:06:29,333 --> 00:06:30,458
A couple's

133
00:06:31,625 --> 00:06:32,625
photoshoot?

134
00:06:34,250 --> 00:06:35,250
You didn't know?

135
00:06:35,458 --> 00:06:36,500
Brother Zhan Wang wanted??

136
00:06:37,291 --> 00:06:38,291
I just wanted...

137
00:06:38,875 --> 00:06:39,875
I realized

138
00:06:40,041 --> 00:06:42,333
we don't even have a
single proper photo together.

139
00:06:42,625 --> 00:06:43,625
Just to have a keepsake.

140
00:06:44,833 --> 00:06:45,833
Okay.

141
00:06:46,208 --> 00:06:47,208
Let's take it.

142
00:06:48,416 --> 00:06:48,875
Bro,

143
00:06:49,166 --> 00:06:50,625
look a bit closer.

144
00:06:51,125 --> 00:06:52,125
Put your arm around him.

145
00:06:52,416 --> 00:06:53,416
Bro,

146
00:06:53,500 --> 00:06:54,767
turn your right cheek a bit more.

147
00:06:54,791 --> 00:06:56,583
Lean your left cheek closer to him.

148
00:06:57,208 --> 00:06:57,791
Just like that.

149
00:06:57,958 --> 00:06:58,791
So sweet!

150
00:06:58,916 --> 00:06:59,416
One more!

151
00:06:59,416 --> 00:07:00,416
Here, take this.

152
00:07:36,916 --> 00:07:37,916
It's beautiful.

153
00:07:38,583 --> 00:07:39,583
Like a painting.

154
00:07:40,791 --> 00:07:42,625
The sea is so beautiful today.

155
00:07:44,500 --> 00:07:45,500
Xu Yuan,

156
00:07:45,791 --> 00:07:46,791
let's make a wish.

157
00:07:47,166 --> 00:07:49,833
Think about what we'll
be doing in ten years.

158
00:07:50,708 --> 00:07:51,708
Okay.

159
00:07:55,291 --> 00:07:56,333
In ten years,

160
00:07:56,618 --> 00:07:59,034
I still want to be with Zhan Wang.

161
00:08:02,250 --> 00:08:03,416
In ten years,

162
00:08:04,833 --> 00:08:06,833
I still want to be with Xu Yuan.

163
00:08:08,541 --> 00:08:11,916
We'll be together forever.

164
00:08:19,916 --> 00:08:20,916
In ten years,

165
00:08:21,083 --> 00:08:22,708
I'm going to be the absolute best!

166
00:08:24,958 --> 00:08:25,958
In ten years,

167
00:08:26,708 --> 00:08:27,875
I hope my clinic

168
00:08:28,750 --> 00:08:30,190
is set up wherever it's needed most,

169
00:08:30,958 --> 00:08:31,958
and the person by my side

170
00:08:33,291 --> 00:08:34,291
is still the same person.

171
00:08:35,791 --> 00:08:37,000
In ten years,

172
00:08:37,125 --> 00:08:39,666
I'll have a sunlit art studio,

173
00:08:39,833 --> 00:08:42,375
painting all the stories and people I want,

174
00:08:44,666 --> 00:08:46,833
and I'll paint the most beautiful posters

175
00:08:47,208 --> 00:08:48,928
for the star who takes on the bigger stage.

176
00:08:49,333 --> 00:08:50,458
In ten years,

177
00:08:51,041 --> 00:08:54,083
I will definitely be a superstar.

178
00:08:54,250 --> 00:08:54,875
When that time comes,

179
00:08:54,916 --> 00:08:56,833
you all must come to see my show.

180
00:08:56,958 --> 00:09:00,166
We must stay together forever.

181
00:09:00,541 --> 00:09:03,416
Together forever.

182
00:09:07,541 --> 00:09:08,541
Let's go.

183
00:10:16,833 --> 00:10:17,958
Who gave you this necklace?

184
00:10:19,750 --> 00:10:21,030
I've never seen you take it off.

185
00:10:29,666 --> 00:10:30,666
Are you jealous?

186
00:10:39,708 --> 00:10:40,708
This...

187
00:10:42,041 --> 00:10:43,375
I won this in a boxing match

188
00:10:43,583 --> 00:10:44,583
in the youth division.

189
00:10:44,958 --> 00:10:45,958
I won it.

190
00:10:46,125 --> 00:10:47,125
No one gave it to me.

191
00:10:49,041 --> 00:10:50,041
It's proof

192
00:10:50,583 --> 00:10:52,000
of the first time I used my fists

193
00:10:53,083 --> 00:10:54,083
to prove myself,

194
00:10:55,166 --> 00:10:56,606
and the first time I had the courage

195
00:10:57,291 --> 00:10:58,291
to be my true self.

196
00:11:17,166 --> 00:11:18,166
Now,

197
00:11:19,250 --> 00:11:20,250
it's yours.

198
00:11:22,250 --> 00:11:23,250
My lucky star.

199
00:11:46,916 --> 00:11:47,916
I want to...

200
00:11:49,625 --> 00:11:50,791
have it engraved on my body.

201
00:12:04,041 --> 00:12:05,041
Since we're happy today,

202
00:12:05,291 --> 00:12:06,625
I'll let you have a beer.

203
00:12:07,541 --> 00:12:08,541
Okay.

204
00:12:18,041 --> 00:12:21,333
Don't you think my brother and
Brother Wang make a perfect match?

205
00:12:22,875 --> 00:12:23,875
They really do.

206
00:12:24,208 --> 00:12:25,208
It's amazing.

207
00:12:25,750 --> 00:12:27,333
Brother Wang's arrival,

208
00:12:27,666 --> 00:12:28,666
and your appearance...

209
00:12:29,666 --> 00:12:32,208
It's like seeing novel plots come to life.

210
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:39,000
Sis,

211
00:12:39,125 --> 00:12:40,125
this is for you.

212
00:12:44,458 --> 00:12:45,458
It's beautiful.

213
00:12:46,041 --> 00:12:47,041
These shells...

214
00:12:47,083 --> 00:12:48,916
I picked them up one by one on the beach,

215
00:12:49,875 --> 00:12:51,583
and made them into a bracelet.

216
00:12:51,791 --> 00:12:52,875
Don't think it's ugly.

217
00:12:53,333 --> 00:12:55,458
I spent ages learning
how to do it from a tutorial.

218
00:12:58,541 --> 00:13:00,375
Let me put it on for you.

219
00:13:12,708 --> 00:13:13,958
Thank you, Xu Nuo.

220
00:13:15,208 --> 00:13:16,208
I love it.

221
00:13:18,208 --> 00:13:19,708
I'll always cherish this time.

222
00:13:24,041 --> 00:13:25,041
Xu Nuo,

223
00:13:25,750 --> 00:13:26,950
I have to go back to Jingzhou.

224
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:30,583
My wrist is mostly recovered.

225
00:13:31,125 --> 00:13:32,166
The doctor said

226
00:13:33,041 --> 00:13:35,041
I just need regular checkups
and physical therapy.

227
00:13:36,416 --> 00:13:38,291
My school exchange period ended long ago.

228
00:13:39,208 --> 00:13:41,541
I've already delayed for too long.

229
00:13:51,833 --> 00:13:52,833
I know.

230
00:13:54,791 --> 00:13:55,791
I can't keep you here.

231
00:13:58,833 --> 00:14:00,250
You never belonged here anyway.

232
00:14:09,333 --> 00:14:10,333
I don't know

233
00:14:10,916 --> 00:14:11,958
if in your heart,

234
00:14:14,166 --> 00:14:15,208
you just

235
00:14:16,666 --> 00:14:17,833
see me as a sister,

236
00:14:18,708 --> 00:14:21,208
or if you actually like me.

237
00:14:23,750 --> 00:14:24,750
And I don't know

238
00:14:25,333 --> 00:14:26,875
what you're really thinking.

239
00:14:30,375 --> 00:14:31,583
So, I think...

240
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:43,000
Actually,

241
00:14:45,333 --> 00:14:47,125
I want to go to Jingzhou with you.

242
00:14:50,083 --> 00:14:51,763
I want to be by your side while you paint.

243
00:14:53,958 --> 00:14:55,291
I want to be with you.

244
00:14:56,708 --> 00:14:57,708
I don't know

245
00:14:59,416 --> 00:15:00,536
if that's what you want too.

246
00:15:52,500 --> 00:15:53,500
Have you decided?

247
00:15:53,916 --> 00:15:55,116
What are you getting tattooed?

248
00:15:55,291 --> 00:15:56,291
A star and a moon.

249
00:15:57,875 --> 00:15:58,875
Why a star and a moon?

250
00:16:00,666 --> 00:16:01,916
Because you said before

251
00:16:02,916 --> 00:16:04,156
you'd take me to see a comet.

252
00:16:05,249 --> 00:16:06,609
We might not make it to a comet,

253
00:16:08,416 --> 00:16:10,416
but the stars and the
moon are there every night.

254
00:16:13,666 --> 00:16:14,666
And I think

255
00:16:15,791 --> 00:16:16,831
you're more like the moon.

256
00:16:17,958 --> 00:16:19,038
I want to keep you with me.

257
00:16:21,083 --> 00:16:22,083
Then I want one too.

258
00:16:23,625 --> 00:16:25,833
I want to get a star.

259
00:16:29,916 --> 00:16:31,083
You're my lucky star.

260
00:16:32,166 --> 00:16:33,166
With you tattooed on me,

261
00:16:35,041 --> 00:16:36,121
I won't fear any hardships.

262
00:16:38,333 --> 00:16:39,333
Okay.

263
00:17:44,875 --> 00:17:46,515
According to the latest observation data,

264
00:17:46,625 --> 00:17:49,207
Comet C/2023 X1...

265
00:17:49,208 --> 00:17:51,416
This is the nutritious meal
made from Xiao Xu's recipe.

266
00:17:51,916 --> 00:17:53,356
Make sure Xiao Wang eats more of it.

267
00:17:54,750 --> 00:17:56,000
Okay, got it.

268
00:17:56,250 --> 00:17:58,059
...is spreading with Hong
Town as the epicenter.

269
00:17:58,083 --> 00:18:00,083
It is currently expected
to crash in a week.

270
00:18:00,250 --> 00:18:01,610
Yours is the only shop still open.

271
00:18:01,958 --> 00:18:03,208
The other shops on this street

272
00:18:03,541 --> 00:18:05,267
have all closed down
and fled to the shelters.

273
00:18:05,291 --> 00:18:06,731
When are you guys planning to leave?

274
00:18:08,125 --> 00:18:10,166
The school hasn't notified us yet.

275
00:18:10,458 --> 00:18:12,178
We'll wait until the kids' schedule is set.

276
00:18:13,277 --> 00:18:15,157
It's all those clickbait
accounts hyping it up,

277
00:18:15,208 --> 00:18:16,374
causing unnecessary panic.

278
00:18:16,375 --> 00:18:18,059
However, this information
has not been verified

279
00:18:18,083 --> 00:18:19,883
and is still undergoing
further confirmation.

280
00:18:20,208 --> 00:18:21,583
The moment of impact will generate

281
00:18:21,708 --> 00:18:24,291
a localized shock equivalent to
a magnitude 5 to 8 earthquake,

282
00:18:24,521 --> 00:18:25,771
and is highly likely to trigger

283
00:18:25,833 --> 00:18:27,790
tsunami waves of 10 to 15 meters high.

284
00:18:27,791 --> 00:18:28,791
The meteorite is coming.

285
00:18:29,458 --> 00:18:30,458
Are we leaving?

286
00:18:34,416 --> 00:18:34,958
Let me think.

287
00:18:35,166 --> 00:18:36,500
Do you think we'll see the comet?

288
00:18:36,750 --> 00:18:38,830
There's still a week left.
What is there to see now?

289
00:18:40,458 --> 00:18:41,934
Did you guys see that
video in the group chat?

290
00:18:41,958 --> 00:18:43,416
It says the comet will crash early.

291
00:18:44,250 --> 00:18:45,708
And the impact of the crash

292
00:18:45,916 --> 00:18:47,309
will be equivalent to a nuclear bomb.

293
00:18:47,333 --> 00:18:49,250
Come on, you actually believe that?

294
00:18:49,750 --> 00:18:51,625
This morning they claimed inside info

295
00:18:51,750 --> 00:18:52,976
that classes would be suspended

296
00:18:53,000 --> 00:18:54,360
and the whole town would evacuate.

297
00:18:54,708 --> 00:18:56,308
But look, classes are still on schedule.

298
00:18:57,666 --> 00:18:58,208
I'm telling you,

299
00:18:58,333 --> 00:18:59,351
this time is really different.

300
00:18:59,375 --> 00:19:00,875
Isn't my brother an astrophysicist?

301
00:19:01,041 --> 00:19:02,281
He called yesterday and told us

302
00:19:02,333 --> 00:19:03,493
to leave as soon as possible.

303
00:19:03,958 --> 00:19:05,398
Is something really going to happen?

304
00:19:06,041 --> 00:19:06,875
Then ask your brother,

305
00:19:07,000 --> 00:19:07,833
if it really crashes,

306
00:19:08,000 --> 00:19:08,750
will it look like

307
00:19:08,875 --> 00:19:10,684
fireworks magnified tens
of thousands of times?

308
00:19:10,708 --> 00:19:11,541
It must be spectacular.

309
00:19:11,708 --> 00:19:12,851
I wonder if we'll get to see it.

310
00:19:12,875 --> 00:19:13,958
Spectacular, my foot!

311
00:19:14,625 --> 00:19:15,958
A 200-meter object crashing down,

312
00:19:16,375 --> 00:19:17,708
plus the shockwave and tsunami...

313
00:19:18,208 --> 00:19:20,088
It's a question if Hong
Town will even survive.

314
00:19:21,083 --> 00:19:22,723
You think you're watching a sci-fi movie?

315
00:19:22,750 --> 00:19:23,750
True, that does sound terrifying.

316
00:19:23,751 --> 00:19:24,958
If that were really the case,

317
00:19:25,166 --> 00:19:26,601
the school would have
suspended classes long ago,

318
00:19:26,625 --> 00:19:28,585
instead of having us sit
here staring at the sky.

319
00:19:29,125 --> 00:19:30,125
Zhan Wang, look.

320
00:19:35,041 --> 00:19:36,583
Zhan Wang will definitely be fine.

321
00:19:37,208 --> 00:19:38,041
I hope so.

322
00:19:38,041 --> 00:19:39,041
Let's hope.

323
00:19:53,291 --> 00:19:54,892
Please don't make things difficult for us.

324
00:19:54,916 --> 00:19:55,916
I promised Brother Wang

325
00:19:55,958 --> 00:19:57,118
that I'd visit him every day.

326
00:19:57,250 --> 00:19:58,250
Please leave.

327
00:19:59,458 --> 00:20:00,778
Just let me see him for a second.

328
00:20:00,875 --> 00:20:01,375
Please leave.

329
00:20:01,500 --> 00:20:02,500
Just one look.

330
00:20:02,958 --> 00:20:03,958
Please just go back.

331
00:20:15,166 --> 00:20:16,686
Could you please bring this in for me?

332
00:20:24,916 --> 00:20:26,316
Zhan Wang, time for your injection.

333
00:20:28,625 --> 00:20:29,958
I'm not taking it. Go away.

334
00:20:35,500 --> 00:20:36,940
Don't touch me! I told you to leave!

335
00:20:44,541 --> 00:20:45,541
Zhan Wang!

336
00:20:45,750 --> 00:20:47,630
I told you not to touch
me! Didn't you hear me?

337
00:20:48,541 --> 00:20:49,541
Calm down.

338
00:20:49,916 --> 00:20:50,916
Please calm down.

339
00:20:55,291 --> 00:20:56,291
Two.

340
00:20:56,375 --> 00:20:57,375
Three.

341
00:20:57,875 --> 00:20:58,875
Four.

342
00:21:01,458 --> 00:21:02,458
Brother Wang!

343
00:21:07,333 --> 00:21:08,333
Brother Wang!

344
00:21:18,875 --> 00:21:19,875
Brother Wang!

345
00:21:20,166 --> 00:21:20,625
Brother Wang!

346
00:21:20,666 --> 00:21:21,666
Come in from over there.

347
00:21:22,833 --> 00:21:23,333
Mr. Zhan.

348
00:21:23,791 --> 00:21:25,226
The young master's emotions are unstable,

349
00:21:25,250 --> 00:21:26,370
and he's refusing treatment.

350
00:21:33,708 --> 00:21:34,708
Let's go.

351
00:21:42,750 --> 00:21:43,750
Dad.

352
00:21:44,875 --> 00:21:45,875
That's more like it.

353
00:21:46,083 --> 00:21:47,283
Just focus on getting treated.

354
00:21:49,041 --> 00:21:50,041
In a few days,

355
00:21:50,291 --> 00:21:51,291
we'll return to Jingzhou

356
00:21:51,583 --> 00:21:53,583
to continue with systematic treatment.

357
00:21:54,250 --> 00:21:55,250
You're still very young.

358
00:21:55,916 --> 00:21:57,516
You still have a long life ahead of you.

359
00:21:57,750 --> 00:21:58,916
Keep this attitude

360
00:21:59,041 --> 00:22:00,142
and cooperate with the doctors.

361
00:22:00,166 --> 00:22:01,166
Understand?

362
00:22:02,291 --> 00:22:03,291
I understand.

363
00:22:17,625 --> 00:22:18,625
Where is your tattoo?

364
00:22:21,125 --> 00:22:22,125
Find it yourself.

365
00:24:29,375 --> 00:24:30,375
Are you leaving already?

366
00:24:32,750 --> 00:24:34,270
I have to go back to school for class.

367
00:24:35,458 --> 00:24:36,458
Don't go.

368
00:24:37,208 --> 00:24:38,208
Alright.

369
00:24:38,708 --> 00:24:40,588
I'll come back to keep
you company after class.

370
00:24:44,208 --> 00:24:45,208
What's wrong?

371
00:24:45,333 --> 00:24:46,083
Do you have a headache?

372
00:24:46,291 --> 00:24:47,291
Should I call the doctor?

373
00:24:51,291 --> 00:24:52,291
It hurts here.

374
00:24:56,375 --> 00:24:57,975
I really don't know what to do with you.

375
00:25:00,041 --> 00:25:01,041
What are you two doing?

376
00:25:02,666 --> 00:25:03,666
Why is he here?

377
00:25:06,541 --> 00:25:07,541
Take him away!

378
00:25:10,125 --> 00:25:11,125
Let go of him!

379
00:25:11,916 --> 00:25:12,375
Brother Wang!

380
00:25:12,458 --> 00:25:13,458
Xu Yuan, I'm fine.

381
00:25:13,583 --> 00:25:14,291
Just focus on your treatment.

382
00:25:14,375 --> 00:25:15,375
Stay right there!

383
00:25:28,791 --> 00:25:30,791
Xiao Wang's condition
is still deteriorating.

384
00:25:31,583 --> 00:25:32,976
The medical facilities in Hong Town

385
00:25:33,000 --> 00:25:34,291
cannot cure him at all.

386
00:25:34,666 --> 00:25:35,875
If you want him to live,

387
00:25:36,041 --> 00:25:37,441
he must be transferred immediately.

388
00:25:38,166 --> 00:25:39,250
Right now, because of you,

389
00:25:39,375 --> 00:25:40,375
he refuses to go back.

390
00:25:40,458 --> 00:25:41,778
He's practically killing himself.

391
00:25:42,750 --> 00:25:43,950
I can go to Jingzhou with him.

392
00:25:44,125 --> 00:25:45,165
How can you accompany him?

393
00:25:45,416 --> 00:25:46,416
In what capacity?

394
00:25:46,958 --> 00:25:47,958
As his boyfriend.

395
00:25:48,708 --> 00:25:49,790
Do you also want him

396
00:25:49,791 --> 00:25:51,500
to be despised by everyone around him?

397
00:25:58,166 --> 00:25:59,333
If you truly care about him,

398
00:26:00,208 --> 00:26:01,208
you should leave him

399
00:26:01,875 --> 00:26:03,195
so he can focus on his treatment.

400
00:26:07,958 --> 00:26:08,958
I understand.

401
00:26:10,541 --> 00:26:11,541
Before he leaves,

402
00:26:12,291 --> 00:26:13,531
don't let him suspect anything.

403
00:26:15,291 --> 00:26:16,583
Just send him off peacefully.

404
00:26:17,291 --> 00:26:18,651
It's for the best for both of you.

405
00:26:44,500 --> 00:26:45,500
Sweetie,

406
00:26:46,041 --> 00:26:47,041
should we take this?

407
00:26:48,583 --> 00:26:49,583
Take that one.

408
00:26:53,125 --> 00:26:53,750
What about these two?

409
00:26:53,958 --> 00:26:54,958
Leave those two behind.

410
00:26:55,916 --> 00:26:56,916
Brother Xu,

411
00:26:58,583 --> 00:26:59,583
Xiao Yuan,

412
00:27:01,958 --> 00:27:02,958
Is Zhan Wang's illness

413
00:27:03,583 --> 00:27:04,583
really that serious?

414
00:27:04,708 --> 00:27:06,028
The technology and equipment here

415
00:27:07,041 --> 00:27:08,201
are already the best we have.

416
00:27:08,291 --> 00:27:10,291
But Jingzhou does have
a more professional team

417
00:27:10,583 --> 00:27:11,903
and more cutting-edge treatments.

418
00:27:12,083 --> 00:27:15,743
Going back is the best,
and only, option.

419
00:27:17,166 --> 00:27:18,166
Our father's methods

420
00:27:19,583 --> 00:27:20,583
might be a bit harsh,

421
00:27:20,958 --> 00:27:22,000
but on this matter,

422
00:27:23,541 --> 00:27:24,541
he isn't lying to you.

423
00:27:30,416 --> 00:27:31,416
The comet is coming.

424
00:27:31,750 --> 00:27:32,750
I received word

425
00:27:34,291 --> 00:27:35,291
that this time,

426
00:27:36,541 --> 00:27:38,301
it's supposed to be
worse than 18 years ago.

427
00:27:39,666 --> 00:27:40,375
Hurry home

428
00:27:40,458 --> 00:27:41,938
and pack your bags with Auntie Meixi.

429
00:27:42,375 --> 00:27:43,375
Bian-bian and I

430
00:27:44,875 --> 00:27:46,115
are also preparing to evacuate.

431
00:27:46,291 --> 00:27:47,291
Okay.

432
00:27:48,958 --> 00:27:51,041
Stop playing and come help.

433
00:27:51,708 --> 00:27:52,500
Mom,

434
00:27:52,625 --> 00:27:53,708
stop packing.

435
00:27:53,875 --> 00:27:55,375
A lot of bloggers have debunked it.

436
00:27:55,541 --> 00:27:57,375
This whole comet thing is a hoax.

437
00:27:59,000 --> 00:28:00,708
Bro, talk some sense into Mom.

438
00:28:00,833 --> 00:28:02,073
She actually wants to evacuate.

439
00:28:02,291 --> 00:28:02,916
How is it possible

440
00:28:02,917 --> 00:28:04,625
for a comet to wipe out the whole town?

441
00:28:11,916 --> 00:28:14,583
"Pack your bags, we need to go.
The comet is coming."

442
00:28:18,416 --> 00:28:19,416
Bro,

443
00:28:19,458 --> 00:28:20,458
what's wrong with you?

